 />\n好似FK8咁用K20C1加8.7KG輕飛輪加快反應<br />\n至少是正確的一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最理想係同M838T, EJ207, RB26DETT, F154取下經&hellip;學吓點用渦輪之餘又上到8000rpm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">RB26DETT去到8200rpm先Cut油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe03d57b0a6360acf28cce227baca743cc7e0c82","tid":286022,"uid":103016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T19:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國30蚊港紙有交易</blockquote><br />\nFocus RS同Golf R都係喎<br />\n之前Megane RS仲要再平d添"}]}